english: I represent Wellspring Inc. here in Dorisburg
chinese: 我代表 Wellspring Inc. 位于多里斯堡

swedish: Jag råkar vara en av deras mest framstående försäljare, globalt sett
english: I happen to be one of their most accomplished salesmen, globally speaking
chinese: 我恰好是他们在全球范围内最著名的销售人员之一

swedish: Oj! Jag ska jobba för er tror jag...
english: Oh! I think I'll be working for you...

swedish: Vilken tur att jag träffade er

english: I just came to town to start working for Wellspring
chinese: 我刚进城，即将开始为 Wellspring 工作

chinese: 是的，这不是一件容易的事

chinese: 如果你这么说的话。我现在要继续前进，但祝你玩得开心！

chinese: 如果您改变主意请告诉我

chinese: 我正在寻找人来帮助我开始为 Wellspring 工作

english: Hmm, I must have lost it...
chinese: 嗯，我想我一定是失去了它......

english: I don't have a credit card

swedish: Så tråkigt då, ha en bra dag!
english: Too bad, have a good day!
chinese: 那么无聊，祝你有美好的一天！

english: Hmm... I think I might be working for you...?
chinese: 嗯...我想也许我应该为你们工作..？

chinese: 有一些方法可以证明你确实是“塞巴斯蒂安”

Nä det har jag nog inte tyvärr

chinese: 嗯，不幸的是我可能没有那个

Jag kanske kan be min mamma att skicka hit en med posten...

chinese: 也许我可以让我妈妈寄一份到这里...

chinese: 但我今天只有时间教你最重要的事情

chinese: 好的，那你什么时候可以告诉我

chinese: 不是？可以的话请告诉我

english: You'll have to start working soon if you want to meet your quota
chinese: 如果你想卖得足够多，你就必须尽快开始工作

english: You're not allowed to be here!!!

chinese: 嘿，我们以前见过面，对吧？

chinese: 只是想认识一些人，刚搬到这里

chinese: 这些天你在这个镇上再多疑也不过分

swedish: Om du inte berättar så berättar inte jag
english: I won't tell if you don't
chinese: 如果你不告诉我，我就不告诉你

english: What? How do you know my name?!
chinese: 啊？你怎么知道我的名字？！

english: Like I said, you have to be pretty paranoid to keep anything a secret around here
chinese: 也就是说，如果你想保守秘密，你就不能只是偏执而已
我的名字是塞巴斯蒂安

english: So Sebastian, what's your calling in life?
chinese: 那么塞巴斯蒂安，你的生活是什么？

english: Eh, I don't know... guess I haven't figured it out yet
chinese: 呃，我不知道……我猜还没弄清楚

chinese: 是的，这很有趣！你想要一个吗？

swedish: Det är inte så kul men det funkar. Du vill inte ha en?

chinese: 这不是那么有趣，但是很有效。你不想要一个吗？

english: I sell soda, but lately I've become a little interested in politics
chinese: 我卖软饮料，但最近我对政治有点兴趣

english: Yeah, there seems to be some kind of movement against the ministry in this city
chinese: 是的，城里似乎有某种反对这个事工的运动

chinese: 果然有反对他们的运动

english: Yes, I think we should dismantle the welfare state
chinese: 是的，我认为我们应该废除福利国家

english: Why should I have to pay just because someone else gets sick?!
chinese: 别人生病了我为什么要付钱？

english: You were so damn secretive is all

english: Gotta go, I'm afraid. I think I'm supposed to meet up with someone soon
chinese: 不，不幸的是我现在必须走了。我想很快就会见到某个人

english: What about you, what are you up to?
OK, so you're in retail like me?
chinese: 好吧，像我这样的销售人员？

swedish: Du ska inte ha en läsk förresten?
english: By the way, do you want a soda?
chinese: 你不应该喝软饮料，是吗？

swedish: Men du, jag måste gå nu
Jag dricker inte såna där saker

english: The ministry's been known to tamper with it
chinese: 众所周知，该部会修改它们

english: Change the code, and so on and so forth

swedish: Vadå, är de inte tillräckligt nyttiga eller?
english: Why, they're not healthy enough or what?
chinese: 什么，它们还不够有用吗？

swedish: Nej då, sånt bryr jag mig inte om
english: No no, I don't care about stuff like that

swedish: Men ministeriet kan ha mixtrat med dem
english: But the ministry may have tampered with it
chinese: 但该部可能对它们进行了修改

english: Or maybe the soda company struck a deal and handle that stuff themselves
chinese: 或者软饮料公司已签订协议并自行处理该部分

chinese: 沿着这里的水流走，稍后你应该会看到一个标志

english: Just don't cross the bridge, or you'll end up in the Burrows
chinese: 不要只过桥，你就会到达陋居

english: Good day to you my good sir, are YOU interested in trying some Wellspring Soda?
chinese: 早上好，先生，您有兴趣尝试 Wellspring Soda 吗？

swedish: Skulle sitta fint med något att dricka, eller hur?
english: Would be nice to have something to drink, right?
chinese: 和喝点东西很配，不是吗？

english: Perhaps you'd be interested in a can of refreshing Wellspring Soda?
chinese: 也许您想买一罐清爽的泉泉苏打水？

chinese: 你想去酒吧喝杯啤酒吗？

english: Nah kid, I'm good, I'm heading home soon
chinese: 不，这是个好孩子，我很快就要回家了

swedish: Du vill inte köpa en läsk av mig?

chinese: 你不想给我买苏打水吗？

chinese: 坐在阳光下放松的完美一天

swedish: Ja, om man inte har viktigare saker för sig så
english: Yeah, unless you've got more important things to do

english: We've been over this a thousand times by now, you know exactly how dangerous it is

english: She's a tad hysterical, as you can tell
chinese: 正如你所看到的，她变得有点歇斯底里

Jag måste få vara själv med Ivan!

我们不能在这里见面吗？

Yes, I suppose it will have to work out...

chinese: 未经授权的人员不得在此停留！

english: Jörgen, looks like we had visitors last night

chinese: 未经授权的人员不得在此停留！

chinese: 软饮料推销员，试用三个月

chinese: 是的，我认为多里斯堡在一个岛上

english: It's a bit unclear actually, somehow

english: Sir, there are a number of other calls I have to make tonight
chinese: 所以，今晚我还有很多电话要接听

swedish: Men om det var allt så tycker jag att vi nöjer oss så
english: But if that will be all...
chinese: 但如果仅此而已，我想我们就这样解决吧

swedish: Vi hoppas att du kommer att trivas i Wellspring-familjen!
english: We hope you'll enjoy being part of the Wellspring family
chinese: 我们希望您喜欢成为 Wellspring 大家庭的一员！

swedish: Eh, så jag fick jobbet alltså?
english: Er, so, I got the job?
chinese: 呃，所以我得到了这份工作？

swedish: Nej nu ska jag kolla på TV hörrni
english: OK guys, I'm gonna watch some TV
chinese: 不，现在我要去看电视 hörrni

english: Who was that on the phone, Sebastian?
chinese: 塞巴斯蒂安电话里是谁打来的？
是的，但是有什么好玩的

english: Real soon, I gotta catch a ship tomorrow morning
chinese: 很快，明天一早我就得坐船去

swedish: Bäst att du sover ordentligt då
english: You better get some proper sleep then

Jag fick ett jobb, det verkar vara i en annan stad
english: I got a job, looks like it's in another city
chinese: 我找到工作了，好像在另一个城市

swedish: Vänta, jag ska bara kolla klart här
english: Hold on, just gonna watch this
chinese: 等等，我只是要检查一下这里

swedish: Det är viktiga saker det här

english: There's a lot going on, out in the world
Haha, that's funny! Look at that!

chinese: 是的，塞巴斯蒂安是什么？

swedish: Jag går och lägger mig nu
Jag ska gå och göra lite läxor på mitt rum
english: I'll go do some homework in my room
chinese: 我要去我的房间做作业

swedish: Jag ska nog gå och lägga mig snart
english: I'll probably go to bed soon
chinese: 我可能很快就会去睡觉

swedish: Hej då, hoppas du får det bra på ditt nya jobb
english: Bye, hope you like your new job
chinese: 你好，希望你在新工作中一切顺利

swedish: God natt, hoppas du kan sova
english: Good night, hope you get a good night's sleep

swedish: Ska du och pappa skilja er?
english: Are you and dad getting a divorce?

swedish: Men Sebastian, varför tror du det?
english: Sebastian, what makes you say that?
chinese: 但是塞巴斯蒂安，你为什么这么想？
